160 BANK 2:POKE$30D,0:POKE$30C,$00:POKE$30E,$A0
170 SYS$8C1E : REM ZSM-SETMEM
180 REM NOW WE'RE CLEAR TO START SONG PLAYBACK
190 POKE$30D,0 : REM PRIORITY (SLOT) 0
200 SYS$8C06 : REM ZSM-PLAY
